      value: You
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[6].speaker
      value: You
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[7].speaker
      value: Cave
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[8].speaker
      value: Cave
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[9].speaker
      value: Cave
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[0].Dialogue
      value: The sky burns. The clouds are gone. The rivers are forgotten.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[0].dialogue
      value: You are not the first to fall through me.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[1].Dialogue
      value: We used to flow freely. Now, the surface consumes us whole.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[1].dialogue
      value: I've seen it all. Bones. Spiders. Things of all sorts. Few of them remain.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[2].Dialogue
      value: These spikes don't seem too friendly . . .
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[2].dialogue
      value: "Who\u2014 who said that?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[3].dialogue
      value: 'I lie all around you. The turbulent floor. The impaling spikes. The
        trembling walls. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[4].dialogue
      value: Speak, what brings you here?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[5].dialogue
      value: I have watched civilizations rise and fall.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[6].dialogue
      value: My family . . . my whole lake . . . all gone. Vaporized into the smoldering
        air.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[7].dialogue
      value: 'A lake. I remember those. They fed me before the world withered away. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[8].dialogue
      value: Now they send mere droplets. One by one.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[9].dialogue
      value: Be the one to make it count.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[0].jumpAllowed
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[0].moveAllowed
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[9].jumpAllowed
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1317100978998197740, guid: 97e88e93d0be8446ca55570b8de282a4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[9].moveAllowed
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
